<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Upa Zasiama</author>
<hymn_number>45</hymn_number>
<title>Aw na thisan achun</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw khawiah him, Hukdampa chun,
 Lungngaih gimtheih A thuok?
 A mel deihum tak muh ka nuom,
 Hehpih thisan luonna.

[V2]
 Aw na thisan luong chu mu leng,
 Ka gitloh nin silthieng intin;
 Lungkham lungzinna bei tana,
 Aw, na thisan achun.

[V3]
 2. Ka hun ngai hi Lalpa tuhin,
 Ka gitloh silthieng di'n;
 Khawvel ahin Nangmah lo chu,
 Thienna dang a um puoi.

[V4]
 3. Ka thihni phat a hungtun tieng,
 Hehpih in ei puiin;
 Lau puong kating thihna lui chu,
 Damin hung kaidawk ka.</lyrics>
</song>